### ====================================================================
### GitHub 代理 API 测试
###   后端代理调 GitHub REST API
###   学习要点: RestClient / DTO / @JsonNaming / ParameterizedTypeReference
### ====================================================================


### 0. 登录 tester1, 捕获 JWT 到 {{token}}
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "tester1",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.data);
%}


### ====================================================================
### 1. 查仓库基本信息 - 正常路径
### ====================================================================

### 1.1 spring-projects/spring-ai
###     期望: 看到 stargazersCount / language="Java" 等真实数据
GET http://localhost:8000/api/github/repos/spring-projects/spring-ai
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1.2 vuejs/core
###     期望: language="TypeScript", 几万 star
GET http://localhost:8000/api/github/repos/vuejs/core
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1.3 torvalds/linux  (内核仓库, 巨大数据)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/github/repos/torvalds/linux
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ====================================================================
### 2. 查仓库活动列表 - 数组响应 (ParameterizedTypeReference 验证)
### ====================================================================

### 2.1 spring-ai 的活动
###     期望: 返回数组, 每条带 pusher 嵌套对象
GET http://localhost:8000/api/github/repos/spring-projects/spring-ai/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.2 spring-boot 的活动 (常活跃, 数据多)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/github/repos/spring-projects/spring-boot/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ====================================================================
### 3. 异常路径测试
### ====================================================================

### 3.1 不存在的仓库
###     期望: code=500 (GitHub 返 404, RestClient 抛异常, GlobalExceptionHandler 兜底)
###     这是预期行为, 暴露"错误处理还没做"的状态, 后续优化
GET http://localhost:8000/api/github/repos/spring-projects/this-repo-does-not-exist-2026
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.2 不存在的 owner
###     期望: code=500 同上
GET http://localhost:8000/api/github/repos/nonexistent-owner-2026/whatever
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.3 不带 JWT (你的 Spring Security 应拦)
###     期望: 401
GET http://localhost:8000/api/github/repos/spring-projects/spring-ai
